{"tid":723310,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[阿根廷全國怒爆] 森柏奧利被揭發購買十六強後當晚即回國的機票！","createTime":"2018-06-30T09:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T17:17:04.000Z","uid":28938,"like":136,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfcd76840ccea938b48c6fcc1bd0c19a95ae72f","tid":723310,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:40:55.000Z","msg":"阿根廷將於北京時間今晚十時迎來對撼法國的十六強大戰。藉分組賽最後一場險勝，加上美斯於中場時間罕有地發表講話，阿根廷球隊精神面貌已有所提升，令人感到這頭南美雄鷹終於甦醒了！<br />\n<br />\n可是好境不常，阿根廷當地有旅行社爆料指出，昨天森柏奧利已在他們公司購買了從俄羅斯回程阿根廷的機票，而時間竟然是十六強賽完結後當晚！<br />\n<br />\n這個消息流出後，阿根廷全國上下暴怒，紛紛指責森柏奧利未打已認輸，世界盃駐俄的阿根廷體育記者們連夜於阿根廷國家隊的酒店外，向阿根廷人主帥討個說法。<br />\n<br />\n對於傳媒的質問，對此森柏奧利略帶委屈地回應到：「上場比賽結束後，某名老大哥球員在更衣室對我說：『光頭佬，踢罷十六強比賽後就沒有你的事了，之後我當領隊，給我滾回家吧。』」<br />\n<br />\n「我知道自己在更衣室已沒有權力了，所以選擇離開，祝阿根廷好運。」阿根廷人最後亦不失君子風度地道。<br />\n<br />\n被問道最後有甚麼說話向這位球隊老大哥說，森柏奧利略帶神祕地說：「Nonono(不不不)，你以為我只買了自己的機票嗎？我亦替他買了，更預備Lays薯片，他媽的有話明晚在機上慢慢談吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/173936_88037992d24577001fc72b8f983e0467.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F173936_88037992d24577001fc72b8f983e0467.png&h=00c15a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Nineup報記者俄羅斯直撃報道]"},{"pid":"11bd19f51b5bb3f5cf17c85af9c34a981fef4940","tid":723310,"uid":14274,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:43:57.000Z","msg":"無睇樓主名"},{"pid":"19f4b3c8f6a3fe945cdad18f4b85fde237f9dd6d","tid":723310,"uid":23385,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:45:37.000Z","msg":"得lays冇可樂<br />\n你想渴死球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaeb2a3c4a07e7808ddc9bbd91b0693e266c9d0","tid":723310,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"NIneup報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4725bc8d784788bb0593c7d22b36c90c20d046","tid":723310,"uid":70439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:46:32.000Z","msg":"Nonono"},{"pid":"3787c2356621421904b9bebb3bf764f202b13ebc","tid":723310,"uid":122013,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"on9 jai"},{"pid":"2feb63cb57a5d552db2a397bc741cf34fc729721","tid":723310,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"他媽的有話明晚在機上慢慢談吧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b17f2bbe809c248f6badc7b7c7856ebfb2239d8","tid":723310,"uid":3244,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79097218b211eb3735c4b5b9606485c4205831a8","tid":723310,"uid":35070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:53:23.000Z","msg":"光頭佬切腹都唔掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c06152464bc9a94d10554038971b8f3d2cbd61b","tid":723310,"uid":14965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"今次馬馬地，得張圖唔錯"},{"pid":"7cc29d289311432eb00e4ad1371a503ef0678796","tid":723310,"uid":25231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"今次有小小悶<br />\n唔夠高潮"},{"pid":"adc7150ca8487a4c5a3f88b04ffce666c593b747","tid":723310,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c06152464bc9a94d10554038971b8f3d2cbd61b","tid":723310,"uid":14965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"今次馬馬地，得張圖唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828ca9b17424e0cd4ebdbf0682ae089a4681b3fe","tid":723310,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"他媽的"},{"pi